                    <span>The is the pinnacle of literary knowledge of "The Toyota Way."  No other book best illustrates the working principles of Toyota's philisophical foundation.  The knowledge derived from this book goes beyond just manufacturing.  The book is enriched with values and core principles that any "good to great" company should or have employed.  The greatest enjoyment from the book, besides the learning, is being able to actually apply and live the Toyota Way.
<br />
<br />Information Technology
<br />wwww.nummi.com</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Required reading for our clients.</div>
